list.item:
Calls upon the parties to comply with all his
decisions and requests in the exercise of his authority under the
Armistice Agreement;

Calls upon the Governments of Israel and Syria to
co-operate with the Chief of Staff to this end and to refrain from any
unilateral action which would prejudice it;

Affirms that nothing in this resolution shall be
deemed to supersede the Armistice Agreement or to change the legal
status of the demilitarized zone thereunder;
